#REMARK SUMMARY
TITLE	A. aeolicus MnmG + tRNA
BIOISIS_ID	MnmG2X
EXP_DESCRIPTION	SAXS data of A. aeolicus MnmG bund to tRNA. To prepare a MnmG-tRNA complex, we mixed A. aeolicus MnmG with a 1.2-molar excess of A. aeolicus tRNALys(UUU) and purified the complex via gel filtration. SAXS data of the fractions containing the MnmG-tRNA complex were afterwards measured using an HPLC setup.
SOURCE_LOCATION	SWING, Soleil, Paris
PUBLICATION	SAXS analysis of the tRNA-modifying enzyme complex MnmE/MnmG reveals   a novel interaction mode and GTP-induced oligomerization, Fislage M,   et al., Nucleic Acids Res. 2014;42(9):5978-92. doi:   10.1093/nar/gku213. Epub 2014 Mar 14.,PMID: 24634441
